@BackendPortalAPI.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5117

### Health
GET {{BackendPortalAPI.Api_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

### Browse profiles
GET {{BackendPortalAPI.Api_HostAddress}}/api/profiles
Accept: application/json

### Validate a membership card
GET {{BackendPortalAPI.Api_HostAddress}}/api/members/validate?membershipNo=CSI-DXB-1001
Accept: application/json
